    },
    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I’m hanging around, killing an hour. I read the whole JBay Open pamphlet cover to cover. Then I meet Vuyo. He hasn’t slept since last night. He’s pretty cracked but I can tell that he’s very switched on still. “What’s the point of sleeping when you’re not comfortable in life”. We talk about all important things in his life: drinking, producing music and range rovers. He gives me his grandmothers number as she’s the most reliable person in his life. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "I’m hanging around, killing an hour. I read the whole JBay Open pamphlet cover to cover. Then I meet Vuyo. He hasn’t slept since last night. He’s pretty cracked but I can tell that he’s very switched on still. “What’s the point of sleeping when you’re not comfortable in life”. We talk about all important things in his life: drinking, producing music and range rovers. He gives me his grandmothers number as she’s the most reliable person in his life. ",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "color": "default"
    },
    "archived": false
