    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Afika is there when I arrive and he’s a good time. He asks if two of his friends can accompany us in the car as they’ve never been to Port St Johns. Lunga and his partner, that they call Lusikisiki after her home town. We share a joke or two and settle in for the drive. It’s pretty pleasant to be driven around these roads by a local - you just surrender to the fact that even though it’s pretty scary all you can do is enjoy it. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "Afika is there when I arrive and he’s a good time. He asks if two of his friends can accompany us in the car as they’ve never been to Port St Johns. Lunga and his partner, that they call Lusikisiki after her home town. We share a joke or two and settle in for the drive. It’s pretty pleasant to be driven around these roads by a local - you just surrender to the fact that even though it’s pretty scary all you can do is enjoy it. ",
