    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I arrive back at Amapondo backpackers and once again receive a warm welcome. I’m in a different dorm this time - and as Sipho points out, with much better showers. This is the most important piece of information here. I find a double shower intended for two people and max out the enjoyment of really cleaning myself for the first time in a week. Clean clothes are magical. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
