        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I pop down to Spar to buy some food for the week at Mdumbi and am back before dark. I ask Sipho for her recommendation and I’m so happy about the beef honey noodles that she brings. There are some locals who engage in a full on poker game, it reminds me of Ramokone Sunday nights. ",
            "link": null
